data.description: Welcome to this exquisite period custom design home, nestled on a sprawling 1.19 acre lot that boasts timeless elegance and meticulous attention to detail. With 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and an array of exceptional features, this property offers the perfect blend of charm and modern amenities. As you step through the crystal door knobs and into the foyer, you'll immediately appreciate the craftsmanship that defines this residence. Double fireplaces that have been converted to natural gas. The cypress windows provide an abundance of natural light, illuminating the red oak flooring that spans throughout the home. The interior boasts 6-panel wood doors, each a testament to the thoughtful design choices made in this home. The heart of this property lies beyond the living spaces, as you'll be drawn to the stunning 17x48 patio. Here, you can bask in the tranquility of your private oasis. Relax by the soothing fountain, catch your favorite shows on the outdoor TV, or take in the serenity of the koi pond. This outdoor haven is a true entertainer's dream. For those with a green thumb, the 16x22 greenhouse offers the ideal space to cultivate your favorite plants year-round. Another alternate gas heater in the veranda that completely warms the house by itself.  These provide an auxiliary heat source in the event of an electricity outage during the winter months.  Security and privacy are paramount here, w/ a 10-foot fence enclosing the entire property and an electric gate at the circular driveway entrance, providing both convenience and peace of mind. In summary, this period custom design home is a rare gem that seamlessly marries classic design elements with modern amenities. From the crystal door knobs to the lush greenery of the greenhouse, every aspect of this property reflects meticulous craftsmanship and an unwavering commitment to quality. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your own. Schedule a showing today.
